#!/usr/bin/env ssc
---
name: conformance-json-deep-import
backends: [int, js, v2]
---

# Deep imported JSON stays bounded

[deepJsonDocument](./lib/json-deep-tree.ssc)

[jsonValue](std/json.ssc)

```scalascript
var cursor = jsonValue(deepJsonDocument)
for _ <- 1 to 18 do cursor = cursor.get("next")
println(cursor.get("value").asString)
println("json-deep-import-complete")
```
